title: Order Book - Manage Business

creator: BJMASC
descriptionHtml:
Manage your Business with Order Book, Udhar Bahi Khata, Expense Manager & Cash Register. 📕

Key features:

► Order Book
► Khata – Udhar Bahi Khata
► Expense Manager
► Cash Register
► Generate transactions in pdf format.

► Order Book : Here user create order with enter shop name, shop no, mobile number, order date and add item list which selected by user. First add item name list in your app and create order by item list. If order complete then delete this order from list and re-create order with different shop. Create Order PDF file & share file.

► Udhar Bahi Khata : Manage your Customer Udhar Bahi khata & create khata PDF. 📕 This app will help you to get back your money. which are borrow from you by your family , friends or customer. This app will take all your record and save your time. This app remind your family , friends or customer that you need to give back money by sms (local sms charge apply if you have free sms pack then no worry). You just need to add entry when you give money and when you need to get back. Also this app calculate each money which are need to get back from other and show you how much money you have to get back. You can also add record if you borrow money from someone.

► Expense Manager: Money Manager helps you track your financial activity efficiently. Its simple design makes it lightweight, straightforward and very easy to use. It’s done in one click, because you don’t need to fill anything except the amount. You need just a few SECONDS daily to save the amount and each spending purpose. No matter where you are just a couple of taps will save your expense. Money management is always complicated and most of the time you get to wonder where did all your money go, luckily, our simple personal finance app can helps you easily manage your money and keep track of your expense. You can stay on top of your money anytime, anywhere.

► Cash Register: Simple Cash Register lets you manage your cash transactions just like bank transactions. You will not have to calculate your cash balance daily. Keeps track of your daily cash balance easily. A person with simple knowledge of smartphones can operate this app. This is very easy to use. If you are an accountant then this is the best app to manage your daily cash transactions and to keep track of your cash balance. This app improves the productivity of an accountant or an individual. You can also use it as a cash register or your wallet manager. You can use it as your monthly budget planner. You can also use it as a simple ledger. You can take reports of your transactions in pdf format. This app is best for tracking your bank balance. This app tracks and prevents your excessive expenses. Best for who wants to make a list of how much money they have, who gave this money, where they spend this pocket money every day and after spending money how much money still we have that also shows.
descriptionShort: Replace your traditional Order Book & Udhar bahi khata by new digital book. 📕

Replace your traditional Order Book by a new digital book. 📕

Manage your Business with Order Book, Khata Book, Expense Manager & Cash Register. 📕

Key features:

➤ Order Book
➤ Khata Book
➤ Expense Manager
➤ Cash Register

Order Book: Here user creates an order with entering the shop name, shop no, mobile number, order date, and add item list which selected by the user. First, add the item name list in your app and create an order by item list. If the order complete then delete this order from the list and re-create the order with a different shop. Create order 𝗣𝗗𝗙 file & share.

Khata Book: Manage your Customer Udhar bahi khata & create khata PDF. 📕 This app will help you to get back your money. which are borrow from you by your family, friends, or customer? This app will take all your record and save your time. You just need to add entry when you give money and when you need to get back. Also, this app calculates each money which is needed to get back from others and show you how much money you have to get back. You can also add a record if you borrow money from someone.

Expense Manager: Money Manager helps you track your financial activity efficiently. Its simple design makes it lightweight, straightforward and very easy to use. It’s done in one click because you don’t need to fill anything except the amount. You need just a few seconds daily to save the amount and each spending purpose. No matter where you are just a couple of taps will save your expense. Money management is always complicated. Most of them wonder where did all your money go. A simple personal finance app can help you manage your money and keep track of your expense.

Cash Register: Simple Cash Register lets you manage your cash transactions just like bank transactions. You will not have to calculate your cash balance daily. Keeps track of your daily Cash Balance easily. A person with Simple knowledge of smartphones can operate this app. This is very easy to use. If you are an accountant then this is the best app to manage your daily cash
transactions and to keep track of your cash balance. You can use it as your
monthly budget planner. You can also use it as a simple ledger. You can take reports of your transactions in 𝐏𝐃𝐅 format. This app tracks and prevents your excessive expenses. Best for who wants to make a list of how much money they have, who gave this money, where they spend this pocket money every day and after spending money how much money still we have that also shows.

Replace your traditional Order Book by a new digital book. 📕

Manage your Business with Order Book, Khata Book, Expense Manager & Cash Register. 📕

Key features:

➤ Order Book
➤ Khata Book
➤ Expense Manager
➤ Cash Register

Order Book: Here user creates an order with entering the shop name, shop no, mobile number, order date, and add item list which selected by the user. First, add the item name list in your app and create an order by item list. If the order complete then delete this order from the list and re-create the order with a different shop. Create order 𝗣𝗗𝗙 file & share.

Khata Book: Manage your Customer Udhar bahi khata & create khata PDF. 📕 This app will help you to get back your money. which are borrow from you by your family, friends, or customer? This app will take all your record and save your time. You just need to add entry when you give money and when you need to get back. Also, this app calculates each money which is needed to get back from others and show you how much money you have to get back. You can also add a record if you borrow money from someone.

Expense Manager: Money Manager helps you track your financial activity efficiently. Its simple design makes it lightweight, straightforward and very easy to use. It’s done in one click because you don’t need to fill anything except the amount. You need just a few seconds daily to save the amount and each spending purpose. No matter where you are just a couple of taps will save your expense. Money management is always complicated. Most of them wonder where did all your money go. A simple personal finance app can help you manage your money and keep track of your expense.

Cash Register: Simple Cash Register lets you manage your cash transactions just like bank transactions. You will not have to calculate your cash balance daily. Keeps track of your daily Cash Balance easily. A person with Simple knowledge of smartphones can operate this app. This is very easy to use. If you are an accountant then this is the best app to manage your daily cash
transactions and to keep track of your cash balance. You can use it as your
monthly budget planner. You can also use it as a simple ledger. You can take reports of your transactions in 𝐏𝐃𝐅 format. This app tracks and prevents your excessive expenses. Best for who wants to make a list of how much money they have, who gave this money, where they spend this pocket money every day and after spending money how much money still we have that also shows.
